OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA cloudy
OL,6,Fstart to the evening in the west but a
OL,7,Fbright end to the day elsewhere.
OL,8,FRemaining dry overnight with
OL,9,Flengthening clear spells. A mild night.
OL,10,
OL,11,CMonday:FA largely dry day with plenty
OL,12,Fof sunshine and feeling warm. Cloudier
OL,13,Fwith a little rain early in the
OL,14,Fevening across northern Perthshire.
OL,15,
OL,16,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FDry
OL,17,Fand bright with plenty of sunshine
OL,18,Fduring this period. Becoming
OL,19,Fincreasingly warm in general, but
OL,20,Fcooler at times along the east coast.
